divs: Sighting DetailsDriving throught Yosemite October 29 with my husband. We pulled to the side of the road and I snapped a shot with my phone. There were no other people around and I saw no bugs. Perhaps this picture is a bug but I thought I would post, maybe others have seen something like it.
Summary: with my husband and stoped to take a piture with my phone and this showed up. Not seen with the naked eye. Didnt not see bugs around, maybe this is.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Yosemite
